HEADWORD: Precognition
<hw>Pre`cog*ni"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>praecognitio</ets>, fr. <ets>praecognoscere</ets> to foreknow. See
