cognition.</def> <rj><au>Fotherby.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>A preliminary examination of
a criminal case with reference to a prosecution.</def>
<rj><au>Erskine.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

